Short:    Laser Race - A Children's Game 
Uploader: neil@albanyis.com.au (Neil McKnight)
Author:   neil@albanyis.com.au (Neil McKnight)
Type:     game/board
Version:  v1.0
Requires: 1Mb Ram

This is game for children aged 5 upwards.  It is a light cycles type game
for 1 player.  You need a joystick and quick reactions.

Features include 25 levels, a level editor program, nice noises and a fast
computer opponent.  You can create your own level disks and pass them on to
your friends.  Has the capability for different scenery, but this is not
included.

Laser Race is placed in the public domain and may be freely distributed. 
